Query.Statement: SELECT DISTINCT 'laporan neraca' as name, a.ret_id, a.ret_group, a.ret_total as total_bulan_ini, COALESCE(b.ret_total,0) as total_bulan_lalu FROM accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group('Laporan Neraca', [@Start_Date], [@End_Date], 1)a LEFT JOIN accounting.get_account_transaction_amount_by_group('Laporan Neraca', [@Start_Date], [@End_Date], 2)b ON (a.ret_group = b.ret_group)

SELECT a.ret_status, a.ret_group, a.ret_sequences, d.name, d.id, 'Jumlah '||a.ret_group as jumlah FROM accounting.get_group_account_by_report('laporan neraca')a INNER JOIN accounting.report_group_detail c ON (a.ret_status = c.name) INNER JOIN accounting.report_group_summary d ON (c.group_id = d.id)

SELECT a.ret_account_id, a.ret_account_code, a.ret_account_name, a.ret_status, a.ret_amount_month_before, a.ret_amount_month_now, a.ret_amount_movement, a.ret_percent_month_before, a.ret_percent_month_now FROM accounting.get_account_in_journal('Neraca', [@Start_Date], [@End_Date]) a

SELECT 'laporan neraca' as name, UPPER(a.company_name) as company_name, 'NERACA' as judul, a.logo, a.address, 'Telp : '||a.phone as phone, 'Email : '||a.email as email, date_part('day', [@End_Date] ::DATE) || ' ' || master.get_month_name([@End_Date] ::DATE) || ' ' || date_part('year', [@End_Date] ::DATE) as period FROM company.company_profile a

SELECT 'laporan neraca' as name, "left"(master.get_month_name(cast(date_trunc('month', [@End_Date]::DATE) as date) - 1), 3)||' '||date_part('year', (cast(date_trunc('month', [@End_Date]::DATE) as date) - 1) - 1) as month_before, "left"(master.get_month_name([@End_Date]), 3)||' '||date_part('year', [@End_Date]::DATE) as month_now

SELECT 'laporan neraca' as name, "left"(master.get_month_name(cast(date_trunc('month', [@End_Date]::DATE) as date) - 1), 3)||' '||date_part('year', (cast(date_trunc('month', [@End_Date]::DATE) as date) - 1) - 1) as month_before, "left"(master.get_month_name([@End_Date]), 3)||' '||date_part('year', [@End_Date]::DATE) as month_now, SUM(a.ret_amount) AS total FROM accounting.get_report_balance_sheet_summary([@Start_Date] ,[@End_Date]) a
